---
// AIHighlight.astro — Updated to reflect real AI certifications and learning focus
---

<section id="ai" class="section-pad wrap">
  <div class="ai-band reveal">
    <div class="ai-inner">

      <div class="ai-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">AI Engineering</span>
        <h3>Dari Web Developer<br/><em>ke AI Builder.</em></h3>
        <p>
          Saya aktif mendalami ekosistem AI Generatif — dari fondasi model, prompt engineering, hingga membangun aplikasi nyata dengan Azure AI, IBM Watson, dan AWS. Lebih dari 28 sertifikasi AI dan tech telah saya tempuh sejak 2023.
        </p>
        <div class="ai-feats">
          <div class="ai-feat">
            <span class="fi" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
            <div class="ft">
              <strong>Generative AI &amp; LLM</strong>
              <span>Azure AI, IBM SkillsBuild, Dicoding — dari fondasi hingga implementasi.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-feat">
            <span class="fi" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
            <div class="ft">
              <strong>Prompt Engineering</strong>
              <span>AWS Foundations of Prompt Engineering + AI Productivity (Hacktiv8).</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-feat">
            <span class="fi" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
            <div class="ft">
              <strong>AI Ethics &amp; Praktis</strong>
              <span>IBM AI Ethics, Introduction to AI, dan penerapan AI untuk produktivitas.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Terminal card — typing animation handled by interactions.ts -->
      <div class="terminal reveal" data-d="2" aria-label="Terminal showing developer profile">
        <div class="term-bar" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="d"></span>
          <span class="d"></span>
          <span class="d"></span>
          <span class="t">~/isnaeni — zsh</span>
        </div>
        <div class="term-body" id="terminal-body" role="log" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Terminal output"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
